msgid ""
"Licentia helps you choose a license for your project, it allows you to check "
"the license's permissions, conditions and limitations, how to add said "
"license to your project and read the full license."
msgstr ""
"Licentia te adjuta a seliger un licentia per tu projecto, illo te permitte "
"verificar le permissiones, conditiones e restrictiones del licentia, como "
"adder licentia dicite a tu projecto e lefer le plen licentia."

